### ============================================================================
### MISC — Abuse Flags, AI Request Logs, Users CRUD, Company Onboarding, Company Admin
### ============================================================================

### ─── Users CRUD — /api/v1/users ────────────────────────────

### List users (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "New",
  "last_name": "User",
  "username": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "TempPass123!",
  "type": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "role_id": 2,
  "billing_currency": "USD"
}

### Update user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Updated",
  "last_name": "Name",
  "username": "updateduser",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "type": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "role_id": 2,
  "billing_currency": "USD"
}

### Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Abuse Flags — /api/v1/abuseflags ──────────────────────

### List abuse flags (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/abuseflags?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get abuse flag by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/abuseflags/{{abuseFlagId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create abuse flag
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/abuseflags
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Suspicious activity: multiple rapid plan generations",
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "flaggedByUserId": {{userId}}
}

### Update abuse flag
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/abuseflags/{{abuseFlagId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Confirmed abuse: multiple rapid plan generations",
  "resolved": true
}

### Delete abuse flag
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/abuseflags/{{abuseFlagId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── AI Request Logs — /api/v1/airequestlogs ───────────────

### List AI request logs (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/airequestlogs?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get AI request log by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/airequestlogs/{{aiRequestLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create AI request log
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/airequestlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "planId": {{planId}},
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "promptTokens": 500,
  "completionTokens": 1200,
  "totalTokens": 1700,
  "status": "SUCCESS"
}

### Update AI request log
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/airequestlogs/{{aiRequestLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "FLAGGED"
}

### Delete AI request log
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/airequestlogs/{{aiRequestLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Company Onboarding (Public) — /api/v1/public/company-onboarding ──

### Submit onboarding request (multipart — requires JSON file + optional CSV)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/company-onboarding
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=co-boundary

--co-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="request"; filename="request.json"
Content-Type: application/json

< ./onboarding-request.json
--co-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="teamMembersCsv"; filename="team.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./team.csv
--co-boundary--

### Initiate payment for onboarding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/company-onboarding/{{companyOnboardingId}}/pay

### Verify payment for onboarding
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/company-onboarding/verify?tx_ref={{txRef}}&transaction_id=

### Get onboarding status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/company-onboarding/{{companyOnboardingId}}/status

### Get pricing preview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/company-onboarding/pricing?credits=100

### Onboarding payment callback (redirect)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/company-onboarding/callback?tx_ref={{txRef}}&status=successful

### ─── Company Onboarding (Admin) — /api/v1/admin/company-onboarding ──

### List onboarding requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/company-onboarding?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get onboarding request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/company-onboarding/{{companyOnboardingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Approve company registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/company-onboarding/{{companyOnboardingId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adminEmail": "admin@tmag.com"
}

### Reject company registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/company-onboarding/{{companyOnboardingId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient documentation",
  "adminEmail": "admin@tmag.com"
}

### ─── Company Admin Auth — /api/v1/company-admin/auth ───────

### Company admin login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "companyadmin@example.com",
  "password": "CompanyAdmin123!"
}

### Company admin logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Company admin me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### ─── Company Admin Management — /api/v1/company-admin ───────

### View team members
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/team-members?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/users?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Create user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@company.com",
  "password": "TempPass123!",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "creditsAllocated": 50
}

### Update user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/users/{{companyUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@company.com",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "employeeStatus": "active",
  "creditsAllocated": 75
}

### Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/users/{{companyUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Restrict user access
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/users/{{companyUserId}}/restrict-access
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restricted": true
}

### Remove employee
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/employees/{{employeeId}}?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Export company data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/export/company-data?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Delete company
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/companies/{{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Company Admin Plans — /api/v1/company-admin/plans ─────

### List credit plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Get credit plan by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/plans/{{creditPlanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### ─── Company Admin API Keys — /api/v1/company-admin/api-keys ──

### List API keys
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/api-keys?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Create API key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Production API Key",
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59"
}

### Revoke API key
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/api-keys/{{apiKeyId}}?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### ─── Company Admin Credits — /api/v1/company-admin/credits ──

### Get company pricing
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/pricing?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Get quote
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/quote?companyId={{companyId}}&credits=100
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Initiate purchase
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/purchase
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "credits": 100
}

### Initiate HR billing purchase
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/purchase/hr
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "credits": 200
}

### Payment callback
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/callback?tx_ref={{txRef}}&status=successful

### Verify purchase
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/verify/{{txRef}}

### Purchase history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/history?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Get purchase by txRef
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/credits/{{txRef}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

