### ─── Company Admin Settings — /api/v1/company-admin/settings ──

### Get company settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/settings?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

### Update company settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "settings": {
    "maxCreditsPerEmployee": {"value": "100", "type": "INTEGER"},
    "requiresDoctorApproval": {"value": "true", "type": "BOOLEAN"}
  }
}

### Update billing currency
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/company-admin/settings/billing-currency?companyId={{companyId}}&currency=USD
Authorization: Bearer {{companyAdminToken}}

